But radio and TV personality Unathi Msengana believes that if you want to get fit, there's no need to wait. The time to start is now. Taking to social media Unathi advised her followers to get started now. "When you ladies say to me 'Yho Unsta I'm gonna start training/running next year.' I'm like Why. Why wait! Why sabotage your success and delay it? Why, why, why if you are unhappy now?," she questioned. She makes some valid points ladies. So rather go easy on those festive treats!A photo posted by Unstagram (@unathi.co) on Dec 12, 2016 at 8:25pm PST 